replies.body:
This sounds a lot like packet loss or high packet buffering, both of which are caused by an unstable connection to the server. Most of the time, this can be resolved by ensuring your local network settings are compatible with League using our [connection guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if those steps helped.
